data.description: Welcome to a wonderful horse facility near Helena, Montana! The proximity to both rural tranquility and town conveniences makes it an ideal balance for families and horse enthusiasts. The combination of a coverall arena, outdoor riding arena, paddocks for boarding, and well-equipped horse barn with stalls, tack rooms, and hay storage provide versatile options for horse care and training. The ranch-style home with four bedrooms, two bathrooms, a family room, and a fireplace make it cozy and inviting. The open floor plan and spacious deck make it perfect for entertaining guests. Watching kids ride in the outdoor arena or observing horses in the irrigated hayfield from the deck adds to the picturesque setting of this property. Call Tara or Michael for more information or your real estate professional.
